      <scopecontent id="aspace_8378f72fdd7d35fcaaa58bc90d30078f">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>The collection includes photocopies of articles with medical themes from historical newspapers created by Bert Hansen while conducting research for a publication on medical history and mass media. Topics include rabies (hydrophobia) and rabies vaccine; Louis Pasteur; diphtheria; smallpox; food safety; prevention of cruelty to animals; and various medical treatments. Most photocopies are from microfilm resources and have been annotated by Hansen.</p>
      </scopecontent>
